C. S. PAUL, as Tax Collector of Volusia County, Florida, W. HOMER SMITH, as Tax Assessor of Volusia County, Florida, and J. M. LEE, as Comptroller of the State of Florida, v. JOHN R. PARKINSON and KATHERINE G. PARKINSON, his wife. 21 So. (2nd) 208

January Term, 1945

March 9, 1945 Division B Chas. W. Luther, for appellants. P. W. Harvey., for appellees. PER CURIAM:

The decree appealed from is affirmed.

CHAPMAN, C. J., BROWN, THOMAS and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
